{"tid":1689399,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［警世］用一句同你講和理非最大嘅武器係咩","createTime":"2019-11-02T19:22:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-03T08:17:48.000Z","uid":90486,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1350b8f5294163863cd9c7051888a710d1d85bdc","tid":1689399,"uid":90486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T19:22:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">係信念</span></span><br />\n<br />\n哈維爾曾經講過，對抗極權嘅最大武器係&rdquo;living out the truth&rdquo;，即係講真話、活出自己信念。<br />\n<br />\n若然作為一個和理非，相信自己有和平集會嘅權利，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你就要最大程度地守住維園和平集會，哪怕食tg或者俾人拉</span></span>（事實上都告唔到啲咩）<br />\n<br />\n若然你認為蒙面法唔合理，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你就每日戴口罩、喺示威現場戴口罩</span></span><br />\n<br />\n若然你覺得社會唔應該馬照跑舞照跳，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你就要罷工參加集會</span></span><br />\n<br />\n若果你認為黑警濫暴，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你就arms free企上最前線對抗，用最大嘅道德感召力量</span></span><br />\n<br />\n民主唔會由天跌落嚟，要靠自己爭取；信念唔係喺酒吧吹噓，係要在生命中實踐。<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">馬丁路德金、甘地、曼德拉並唔係會喺和平集會現場被清場時恐慌性走嘅人，因為佢地堅守自己嘅理念同價值觀。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n「光復香港，時代革命」唔係廉價口號，而係一個值得活出嘅信念，亦係我地嘅盼望。和勇本是同根生。<br />\n<br />\n希望大家明我想講咩。"},{"pid":"247a6f9af25c1469352cebf1c3b14d763ab2287f","tid":1689399,"uid":90486,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T19:25:41.000Z","msg":"其實講得好厚道，如果話自己和理非但連和平集會都唔出現唔守護嘅，根本無資格話自己係和理非"},{"pid":"ced34d3f60cbf42dc85e8e7689d1a2c0ba2d18df","tid":1689399,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T19:26:29.000Z","msg":"甴近平<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n[品葱] 蔥友幫我哋整咗個backup區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1689247\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1689247</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a49d36cdd8b6943935bacc924e4a661ace59eea9","tid":1689399,"uid":90486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T19:29:56.000Z","msg":"睇嚟無人明，算鳩數，由得「和理非」繼續「和理非」"},{"pid":"637f420757d70c13c1156303b3dab65e94d501b5","tid":1689399,"uid":80162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T19:45:56.000Z","msg":"信念<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地一定要堅持住"},{"pid":"6ff322ebe6d242f7056df188308da9e94572f405","tid":1689399,"uid":186851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T19:49:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a4362819e976c69f0b249aa87cdaa93ae8eb4a07","tid":1689399,"uid":90486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T08:17:48.000Z","msg":"甴近平"}]}